data.text: @TIME Seriuously.. y’all are trying to sell this is a “revolutionary pick” yet the REAL story is they are not paying her the same salary or even close to what Lauer got. This is a empty gesture by @TODAYshow especially with all the talks about #meetoo & workplace equality.
